      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that still turns heads? This beauty has been well-loved and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend getaway. It runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin, I just know you're going to love how it handles!",
