    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Silver Grey Metallic. At the heart of this machine is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that ensures linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing precise gate engagement. Crucial enthusiast-grade maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a top-end refresh to ensure valvetrain longevity. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and a limited-slip differential that provides excellent corner-exit traction. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain and suspension geometry are dialed in for peak performance. A driver-spec example that prioritizes mechanical integrity over concours aesthetics.",
