    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior finish presents beautifully, with a deep gloss that shines in the sunlight; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small hairline scratch near the trunk lid, the body is straight and free of any major dents. Step inside to an interior that feels remarkably fresh. The premium upholstery is clean and intact, showing only slight softening on the driver's side entry point. Every electronic component, from the premium audio system to the heated seats and navigation, is in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and pulls strongly, backed by a comprehensive service history. We recently performed a multi-point inspection, confirming the suspension is tight and the transmission shifts seamlessly. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were recently serviced. This car offers a reliable, high-quality driving experience for its next owner. Comes with two sets of keys and all original owner manuals.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
