    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s still got so much life left in her! It\u2019s been well-maintained, runs like a dream, and is perfect for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks sharp on the road. I've truly enjoyed every mile, and I know you will too. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
