    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 V8 power plant. This unit remains naturally aspirated, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides lightning-fast gear changes, while the Servotronic steering and M-variable differential lock ensure precise turn-in and corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, mitigating common S65 failure points. The chassis remains taut with no bushing deflection, and the EDC (Electronic Damper Control) system functions perfectly across all damping maps. Minor cosmetic stone chipping present, consistent with a well-driven enthusiast vehicle, but the structural integrity and drivetrain performance are top-tier.",
